data.description: Discover elegance in this stunning English-style home,nestled on this 4-acre estate in AISD.Boasting 3 stories of exquisite design,this 2-2 is a treasure of premium features and character;Timeless architecture shows its refined charm and grand presence.A chef's paradise awaits a state-of-the-art gas top stove,ornate gas fireplace,beautifully crafted cabinetry,spacious island perfect for entertaining and culinary creations.The heart of the home shines with a second cozy fireplace soaring ceilings,and ample space for gatherings and relaxation;gleaming hardwood floors throughout the entire home;period-appropriate fixtures featuring a pull chain toilet and a classic clawfoot tub,ensuring in the luxurious bathroom.Connect with nature in the bright sunroom,joining the main house to the garage,a tranquil space for the days end.The basement provides space with endless potential to fit your lifestyle.Above the garage area lies an unfinished guest suite ready for your own complete touches.
